## ğŸš« .gitignore Highlights

Weâ€™ve excluded the following to reduce bloat and avoid committing platform-specific or system-generated files:

- `Library/` â€” Unity cache and metadata
- `Builds*/` â€” Platform-specific build folders
- `mobile/Libraries/libiPhone-lib.a` â€” iOS binary (over 100MB, ignored to prevent GitHub push errors)
- `*.xcworkspace` and `*.xcodeproj` â€” Generated by Unity/iOS builds
- `Temp/`, `Logs/`, `UserSettings/` â€” Local config and debug files

If your project fails to build due to missing packages or files, check the **Package Manager** inside Unity and re-import whatâ€™s missing.

